# Claude settings
# Default: ignore everything under .claude/ ...
.claude/*
# ... but keep shared automation (hooks, skills, settings, commands).
# Personal/runtime files (settings.local.json, worktrees/, scheduled_tasks.lock,
# .coverage, etc.) remain ignored via the leading `.claude/*` rule.
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/hooks/
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/README.md
